article_title: Snow totals from Thursday's winter storm
article_text:
Below are the unofficial snow totals from the wet winter storm on Jan. 7.

Pima County

Summerhaven - 14"

Catalina - 0.5" to 0.8"

Corona de Tucson - 0.2"

Vail - Trace

Cochise County

Beatty's Guest Ranch (Miller Canyon, Huachuca Mountains) - 8.75"

Bisbee - 6"

Mescal - 1"

Pearce-Sunsites - 0.2"

Pinal County

Oracle - 3.5" to 4.5"

Saddlebrooke - 1.8"
